attributionInfo.brokerName: eXp Realty of Greater Los Ange

data.description: Great starter home or investment property.  Corner of Kiowa, although house faces Puye Rd and is set back from Kiowa Rd.  Nice floor plan with all 4 bedrooms off hallway and separate from living areas.  Fireplace in family room, Kitchen has upgrades, dining off kitchen and patio door leads to garage access and covered patio.  Skylight in hall bath, twin pack for heat/air on roof has recently been serviced.  Owner is including LG refrigerator.  Two solar systems both Sunrun $87 and $149 month lease contract.  Seller relocating and has no contingency on purchasing new home.  Large lot fenced with perimeter block and wood fencing.  Windows and twin pack have been replaced.  There is a custom steel screen door.  Laundry hook-ups in garage.  There is parking on concrete driveway and additional space on side of garage.  There are not many 4 bedroom homes available in this price range.
